
Database migration/seed
-----------------------
./artisan migrate:make
./artisan migrate:make create_initial_tables
./artisan migrate:rollback
./artisan migrate:reset
./artisan migrate

./artisan migrate:refresh
./artisan db:seed
./artisan db:seed --class=ProdDatabaseSeeder

Create package
--------------

add name, email to app/config/workbench.php
./artisan workbench arjus/mypackage --resources

create service class and facade.
in service provider, instantiate service in register() and add alias in boot().
register service provider in app/config/app.php

repository: https://packagist.org



.jsp => .blade.php
------------------

s: \$\{([a-zA-Z.]+)\}
r: {{{ $\1 }}}

